description:
Final round! Bryn Blayne and Ariel X go head to head against Penny Barber and Bella Rossi.This round will determine the winners, who will go on to brutally fuck and humiliate the losers.
Round 2 ended with Ariel and Bryn up by 308 points - can Team Blue catch up?
title: May Tag Team Match-up: Round 3 Clash of The Titans!!!
